categories: Category:Cut content from Star Wars Galaxies

nodes.text: Sayama Edosun was a Human female resident of Naboo who lived during the time of the Galactic Civil War.

Sayama Edosun appears in the directory tree files for the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided. According to these files, Sayama Edosun would have been on Naboo. However, Sayama Edosun is not known to have appeared on the video game's live servers as a proper non-player character. Nevertheless, an emulated depiction pulled from this character's Interchange File Format reveals what she would have looked like if she were added to the game.
